programme.title: Olympics 2018: Snowboarding, Curling (Mixed Doubles Semifinal #1)
programme.desc: Women snowboarders hit the course vying for gold in slopestyle, plus a semifinal in mixed doubles curling. programme.desc: Jacksonville Jaguars (11-6) at Pittsburgh Steelers (13-3) in an AFC Divisional game. From Heinz Field. Seven of Pittsburgh's eight Pro Bowl players are on offense, while the Jags have four on defense. The Steelers have eight playoff wins since a divisional-round loss here to Jacksonville 10 years ago in Mike Tomlin's postseason debut. (cc)(n)
